{"tid":410640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終於搵個比地盤佬更臭既物種","createTime":"2017-09-23T06:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T10:29:43.000Z","uid":21970,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbd04faee5ccb5d7ff9bd37cd4880aa054fbb68","tid":410640,"uid":21970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"當連登仔仲為緊地盤佬應唔應該沖完涼先搭車<br />\n小弟今日係地鐵終於解開依個迷團<br />\n如果地盤佬要沖完涼先入得茶記<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有蝻應該永久禁止出街</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母仲要係出左汗既死蝻蟲</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝻鬼獨特既臭加上汗味 帶出又咸又酸既千古奇臭</span></span></strong><br />\n你話我種族歧視都好<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地盤佬無罪 蝻亞佬死全家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9d4678526a933cba74aa39026026f64d02b12ccf","tid":410640,"uid":21970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d897a4c485cbe51532d1ed5cd744e120b3af4655","tid":410640,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"未入嚟已經諗到係佢哋，佢哋真係好大陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b29dca79994c9d0d739fb7ea3edbfa382086d61","tid":410640,"uid":109983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"肥婆"},{"pid":"7d6af6176c317580e5a56e6307e909514987e59f","tid":410640,"uid":21970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未入嚟已經諗到係佢哋，佢哋真係好大陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係隔離坐左5分鐘 臭到依家都覺得有陣徐"},{"pid":"7f96f071d60e5023d62e3f82260552d77e98a7b9","tid":410640,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"佢地好興查個d椰油係個頭度 陣味勁撚臭<br />\n另一樣